notes.qsl_service: *  Indicates current list of entities for which QSLs may be forwarded by the ARRL membership Outgoing QSL Service.
notes.third_party_traffic: #  Indicates entities with which U.S. Amateurs may legally handle third-party message traffic.
notes.antarctica_special: Also 3Y, 8J1, AT0, DP0, FT8Y, LU, OR4, VK0, R1AW, VP8, ZL5, ZS1, ZX0, etc.  QSL via country under whose auspices the particular station is operating.  The availability of a third-party traffic agreement and a QSL Bureau applies to the country under whose auspices the particular station is operating.
